## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] `wok run recipes/pad_thai.wok` exits 0 and produces formatted step-by-step output
- [ ] `wok run recipes/carbonara.wok` and `wok run recipes/omelette.wok` both succeed
- [ ] Referencing an undeclared ingredient raises `PantryError` with the correct line number
- [ ] `crack(rice_noodles, into=wok)` raises `KitchenError` (only eggs can be cracked)
- [ ] `pytest` passes; coverage >80% on `lexer.py` + `parser.py`
- [ ] README contains a complete recipe + its rendered output
- [ ] Total LOC under 800 (target ~500–700). If you're over, you're over-engineering.

